Class Textbox

java.lang.Object
com.dougnoel.sentinel.elements.Element
com.dougnoel.sentinel.elements.Textbox
public class Textbox extends Element
Textbox implementation of a Element. Needed because the text in a text box is stored in a different place than all other elements.
